  <name>Midterm: Notes & Flashcards</name>
  <developer_name>Minh Loi</developer_name>
  <summary>A free note-taking app for self-learning</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>LicenseRef-proprietary</project_license>
  <url type="homepage">https://midterm.app</url>
  <description>
    <p>Midterm is a note-taking app for you to write notes and study them in one place. It includes cloze deletion and image occlusion (inspired from Anki) to help you memorize information better.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Write interactive notes for reviewing (using image occlusion, cloze deletion, etc.)</li>
      <li>Keep track of difficult notes to review before exams.</li>
      <li>Collaborate and study with your friends.</li>
      <li>Organize notes with nested folders.</li>
      <li>Study offline.</li>
      <li>and many more.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
